# PalJS Packages Structure

PalJS is organized as a monorepo with multiple packages in the [packages/](mdc:packages) directory:

## Core Packages
- [cli](mdc:packages/cli) - Command-line interface for PalJS
- [create](mdc:packages/create) - Project scaffolding and initialization
- [generator](mdc:packages/generator) - Code generation utilities
- [schema](mdc:packages/schema) - Schema definition and management
- [plugins](mdc:packages/plugins) - Plugins for extending functionality

## UI and Integration
- [admin](mdc:packages/admin) - Admin UI components and utilities
- [display](mdc:packages/display) - Display components for UI
- [nexus](mdc:packages/nexus) - Integration with Nexus GraphQL framework

## Common Utilities
- [types](mdc:packages/types) - TypeScript type definitions
- [utils](mdc:packages/utils) - Shared utility functions
